Data Types List

Here are the data types with brief descriptions:
cdata::gridMesh structure - normal and superfluid velocities are calculated on the mesh which runs from -box_size /2 to box_size/2 to with mesh_size^3 points, note by setting mesh_size>0 mesh is switched on mesh velocities calculated every mesh_shots timesteps
tree::nodeTree structure, uses pointers
normal_fluid::norm_fluid_gridNormal fluid mesh - all grid based normal velocities use this (e.g. Navier Stokes future)
